data.meta_description: SaaS Cloud-Based Platform for Desktop Software
data.text:
GeoCloud Ltd., the developer, owner and operator of the cloud-based platform www.geocloud.work, is the authorized distributor of certain preinstalled and ready for use commercial software, with licenses from the commercial software vendors listed at www.geocloud.work.

All open-source software is installed and used under open source and free software licenses (such as, for example, the GNU General Public License), which authorizes GeoCloud to make commercial use and distribution of the software.

If you need more information on this matter please register and contact us.
